Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:09.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:12.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:16.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:24.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:48.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:56.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:10.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:21.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:25.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:29.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:32.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who are you?\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Who the heck are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:01:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they also your subordinates, Captain Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.86,0:02:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?! Y-Yeah, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys lost your memories, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.32,0:02:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, pretty ladies! Your names, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a deer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, human! I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates this, pirates that! What a stupid era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate pirates! What I like\Nare money and tangerines!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that I'd\Nbe traveling with pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're making quite a\Nracket so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're interrupting my morning nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get out of here somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no idea what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems like there's\Nno point in me staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:56.99,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"A Mysterious Boy with a Horn\Nand Robin's Deduction!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navigator...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.01,0:03:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can rest easy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that unpleasant pirate\Nhunter is off the ship, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that Navigator\Nmight set foot on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.97,0:03:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing her, she probably won't do too much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until she can make a level-headed decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm starving. I wanna eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... You have no sense of tension, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, I guess we can think about\Nwhat to do after we finish eating, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Miss, I didn't get your name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, could you tell us about\Nthe memories that we lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that I'd stay in a place\Nlike that for even a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates cold-bloodedly steal\Nthings that people cherish!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to come up with a way to\Nreturn to Cocoyashi Village quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad... that you came, lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's awfully quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll find something\Nif I go up a bit higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! This newspaper is\Nthe only thing I can depend on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Stop screwing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I give you something to go on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.27,0:05:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who cares?!\N--Hey, who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew, I wouldn't be having this problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So you're looking for a boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--The boats docked at this harbor\Nare the only boats on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all seem to be in disrepair, as if\Nthey haven't been used in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that everyone is too busy\Nwith other things to care about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't believe me, go ahead\Nand go around the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a small island. It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take it easy and stay a while.\NI'm sure you'll enjoy it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, I see.\N--I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten kinda sleepy. I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are real pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So clouds are really fluffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:07:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daaachshund... Horsey-Bird...\NDarn it! Why can't I remember them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Davy Back Fight, the large Navy fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky islands and the sand country, Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really had such a grand journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain of this ship has a\N100-million-Berry bounty on his head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you have some\Nmore neat adventure stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I joined your crew after you left Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, unfortunately, I don't know\Nwhat happened before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.02,0:07:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I have a hard time buying her story,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is true that the seasonings and equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are where I would like them to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-san, could you tell us about the\Nmost crucial thing-- about yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Well then, let's include\Nthe ship's doctor, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it's backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hungry, aren't you?\NCome and eat with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.18,0:08:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Don't be ridiculous!\NI can't eat with humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask your opinion, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, our exceptional ship's doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy! Praising me wouldn't\Nmake me feel happy! You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure looks happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were traveling this area of sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, are you really sure\Nwe're on the right track?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. The Log Pose\Nis pointing this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Can't you see anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err, hold on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Ah! I see an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are coral reefs scattered all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to keep heading ashore like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drop anchor off the coast\Ntonight and land tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you don't\Nwanna listen to your navigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun, Luffy won't be having dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Okay, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, everyone went to bed except\Nfor me, as I was doing some research,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the swordsman, who was standing watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's not much, but that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is what you remember... probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given the way the pirate hunter talked earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seems he fell asleep\Npartway through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like another cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I wonder why only you\Ndidn't lose your memory, Robin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the swordsman was really asleep,\Nthe only difference between you guys and me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.27,0:09:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is that you were sleeping and I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I was asleep, I remember!\NI'm certain that we're the Usopp Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, sleep determined\Nwhether we lost our memory or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just stated the facts, that's all.\NI can't draw any conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of such a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me the very last thing you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I went to pick\Nmedicinal herbs with Doctorine,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,returned to the castle and went to bed.\NAnd then, when I woke up, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for me... Hey, you're ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fainted after being\Nswallowed by a big whirlpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the next thing I knew, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I went to bed in my room after work,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when I woke up, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't remember\Nanything after those points, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I heard the sound\Nof a horn from somewhere and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A horn... Yeah, a horn! I heard it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child suddenly appeared before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... It's not that\Nwe lost our memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but in fact, that the kid\Nstole our memories from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's certain that he\Nholds the key to this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:10:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it possible that we'll lose more\Nmemories each time we fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:10:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahhhh!\N--Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait. It happened in my dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A supernatural thing like that\Ncan't actually happen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how do you explain the fact\Nthat we all had the same dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supernatural or not, it's the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to scare you,\Nbut in the worst-case scenario,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's possible that you will no longer\Nbe able to tell who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why do you care if we\Nremember things or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it sucks that I lost all those fun memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we can just start over and go on\Nnew adventures together, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be ridiculous! We may\Nend up losing all our memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-If that happens, our past\Nand dreams will all be--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.02,0:11:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream won't be lost. It must\Nbe the same for you guys, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a positive thinker he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.74,0:11:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our captain is the same...\Nwhether or not he has his memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's kinda amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! My food is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch other people's food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.38,0:12:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if he's crazy or what...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I feel like I'm an idiot for\Nthinking about things seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.69,0:12:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kinda exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you making?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A new medicine for regaining\Nmemories! Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Did you find something?\N--Ahhh! Don't touch that without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:13:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No. It seems like an ordinary island.\N--Ugh! What the heck is this? It's bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is, indeed, my great invention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for asking! Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we don't have to worry\Neven if we lose our memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I name them, "My name board"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A question mark? That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a raccoon dog or emergency food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Stupid Lovelyn"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like my idea? Cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make stupid stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories... huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are such fragile things, Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.81,0:13:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, Zoro. You're a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be the world's\Ngreatest swordsman, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:14:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, when girls grow up,\Nthey get weaker than men...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only... If only I had been born a man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be whining like that after you beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair! You're my goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Zoro...\N--Boy this, girl that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna say that stuff\Ntoo when I beat you someday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You act like none of it is skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're insulting all the hard\Ntraining I've been doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't say that stuff! Promise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, one of us will be\Nthe world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll compete to see who gets there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy. You're so weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have... that sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuina's sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get stronger for her, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get strong enough\Nthat my name reaches to Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be the world's\Nstrongest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:15:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave Kuina's spirit and dreams... with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I trained hard every day\Nand set out to sea to search for that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiming to become a master swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.58,0:15:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got on a boat and went to sleep.\NI remember up to that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that... I can't remember\Nwhat happened after that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's weird, in the first place, is these swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When on earth did I obtain these two swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, they suit me quite well.\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most current date on the logbook\Nis the day before the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's consistent... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.71,0:16:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it... Is what\Nthat woman said all true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a member of a pirate group...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's... There's no way that's the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this tattoo... What on earth happened to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be in excellent spirits,\Npathetic humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of this moment,\Nthis island is under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On this memorable day, you will\Nall buy your lives from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.42,0:16:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can't pay... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... want to live in this village...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because we're poor that I can't\Nbe Bellemere-san's kid anymore?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.31,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That 100,000's for my two daughters.\NI don't got enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere! What are you--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Gen-san. I just can't\Nsay I don't have a family...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it costs me my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe we're not related by blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we're a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be their parent,\Neven if it's only in name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're... my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I was never able to\Ndo anything mother-like for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need anything! Just don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make your dream... come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die with your pathetic love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm joining the Arlong Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be a surveyor and draw sea charts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made an agreement with Arlong\Nto buy Cocoyashi Village from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To buy the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For 100 million Berries. If I buy\Nthe village, we can be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, 100 million Berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure you can earn that\Nmuch working your entire life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will earn it! No matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.57,0:18:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ask for help from anyone,\Nmore people will get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll hurt, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:19:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Staying with the people who\Nkilled Bellemere-san'll hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you survive, lots of fun things will happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine. I'll put on a big smile,\Neven when I see his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided not to cry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to fight on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll steal all the rest... All the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I wake you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No...\N--You can go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I notice something unusual, I'll wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Sorry, Robin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I make some coffee to help us stay awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. That would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, he's sleeping like a log,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after saying that he was gonna\Nstay awake no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.61,0:20:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you two weren't asleep yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you who stole everyone's memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you've noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Everyone, wake up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I see you have some mysterious technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahhh!\N--What? Breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't nice, lady.\NTo think that you woke them up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it can't be helped now.\NI didn't wanna do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.78,0:20:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--I'm not gonna let you take that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:21:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that that place is my special seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sit there without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa?! Wh-What's this? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't he in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:22:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:35.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! My memories are back!\NYou are all my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cook, swordsman, navigator,\Ndoctor, scholar, and... liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.34,0:23:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey...\N--Well then, we'll go bring back Nami and Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.97,0:23:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally agree about Nami-san,\Nbut we don't need that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Right, we don't.\N--I guess we don't. No! We do!
